{"tid":2437685,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"范徐麗泰：一國兩制中「兩制」指經濟制度而非政治制度","createTime":"2021-03-08T04:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T05:21:17.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9a89bf07284b8371dc2ee9906c75fb4f0e90f1ed","tid":2437685,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:29:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579217-20210307.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579217-20210307.htm&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058rYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=827dc3f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579217-20210307.htm&h=4cb5ff33\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579217-20210307.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n全國人大前常委、立法會前主席范徐麗泰接受內地傳媒專訪時表示，「一國兩制」中的「兩制」，她認為是經濟制度、金融開放的制度，而不是政治制度。因為要改變政治制度，需要經全國人大常委會通過或者備案才能實施。<br />\n<br />\n范徐麗泰談及人大審議有關完善本港選舉制度的決定議案時表示，目前香港的趨勢已經偏離《基本法》的原意，因此要回看歷史，回歸「一國兩制」的初心；香港運行的選舉制度不可行，會將香港的繁榮安定付諸流水，形容本港已經被逼到懸崖邊。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，到了今時今日，為了香港和國家，已經沒辦法再忍，只能完善選舉制度，將一些不愛國、不願接受憲法和《基本法》、不願意為香港繁榮安定努力的人置之門外。"},{"pid":"684315702a160290a6132383a720cb94299c1a84","tid":2437685,"uid":47259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:18:08.000Z","msg":"人無恥則無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ee1d2de5436959dd4f6e2692203e6a450b27ce","tid":2437685,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T05:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" cl